OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWarm away from the coasts, with
OL,6,Fthe Central Belt seasonally very warm.
OL,7,FSoutheast winds fresh around coasts,
OL,8,Fpegging back temperatures around the
OL,9,Feast coast. Staying dry with sunny
OL,10,Fspells which turn hazy during the
OL,11,Fafternoon as higher cloud increases.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud thickening to bring
OL,14,Foccasional rain, this focused across
OL,15,Fwestern areas of Central and Tayside,
OL,16,Fwith little expected to penetrate to
OL,17,Fthe coast. Southerly coastal winds
OL,18,Finitially fresh.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
