OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCoastal districts milder
OL,6,Fthan today. Elsewhere significantly
OL,7,Fcooler. Rather cloudy morning with
OL,8,Fsome patchy rain, mostly confined
OL,9,Facross the far west. Mainly dry for
OL,10,Fthe afternoon with brighter spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,13,Fearly Thursday, clearing to brighter
OL,14,Fspells and showers for the afternoon.
OL,15,FFriday turning wet and windy with best
OL,16,Fof shelter in east. Showers Saturday,
OL,17,Fmore frequent in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
